sentence: Among the underlying components of the S&P 500 index, we saw noteworthy options trading volume today in Pfizer Inc (Symbol: PFE), where a total of 128,885 contracts have traded so far, representing approximately 12.9 million underlying shares.
That amounts to about 57.2% of PFE's average daily trading volume over the past month of 22.5 million shares.
Especially high volume was seen for the $36 strike call option expiring June 19, 2020, with 4,516 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 451,600 underlying shares of PFE.
